videos.description: North Carolina's Seventh Woods lobs a pass up to Garrison Brooks, who elevates for a two-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Woods finds Brooks for the alley-oop

videos.description: North Carolina's Brandon Huffman backs his way to the basket and banks in the layup.
videos.headline: Huffman muscles his way for easy bucket

videos.description: North Carolina's Cameron Johnson pulls up from a few steps behind the 3-point line and knocks down the shot.
videos.headline: Johnson connects from way downtown

videos.description: Louisville's Christen Cunningham drives around defenders to the basket and drops in the layup while drawing a foul.
videos.headline: Cunningham flies to rim for and-1

videos.description: Luke Maye gathers a loose ball on defense and then has a wide-open lane at the other end for a two-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Maye flies to the rim for easy dunk
